sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as React Frontend<br/>(AI Panel)
    participant IPC as Tauri IPC<br/>(Command Handler)
    participant CTX as Context Builder
    participant RED as Redaction Engine
    participant API as ClaudeApiPort<br/>(Anthropic HTTP)
    participant Claude as api.anthropic.com

    User->>UI: Natural language query<br/>"find large files over 100MB"
    UI->>IPC: invoke ai_translate_command(query, shell_context)
    IPC-->>UI: returns request_id

    Note over IPC: Spawns async Tokio task

    IPC->>CTX: Build prompt from shell_context<br/>(cwd, shell_type, OS, recent cmds)
    CTX->>RED: Filter assembled context
    RED->>RED: Apply regex patterns<br/>(API keys, passwords, PII)
    RED->>API: send_message_with_tools(prompt, callbacks)
    API->>Claude: HTTPS POST /v1/messages<br/>(streaming, tool_use mode)

    loop SSE Stream
        Claude-->>API: Server-Sent Event chunk
        API->>IPC: callbacks.on_chunk(text)
        IPC-->>UI: emit ai:stream-chunk(request_id, text)
        UI->>UI: Render streaming text
    end

    Claude-->>API: tool_use: suggest_command
    API->>IPC: callbacks.on_tool_use("suggest_command", input)
    IPC-->>UI: emit ai:tool-use(request_id, suggestion)
    UI->>UI: Show command suggestion<br/>with risk level + confirm/reject

    API->>IPC: callbacks.on_completion(metadata)
    IPC-->>UI: emit ai:stream-end(request_id, metadata)

    User->>UI: Confirms suggested command
    UI->>IPC: invoke write_to_pty(session_id, command_bytes)
